                            <td colspan="4" style="text-align: center; font-weight: 600; color: #f44336; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">DIVIDING LINE: INVESTMENT GRADE VS JUNK</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Non-Investment Grade (Speculative)</td>
